Description: "Tomorrowland"
Written and Produced by Abyss for Moodswingz Muzik.
A hypothetical yet relatable tale of
a young man who has a lot going for himself
who, due to foolish pride and negative mental conditioning,
makes a fatal decision
that would ultimately shape the rest of his days.
Tomorrowland is the Genesis CNFT release from
Abyss and Moodswingz Muzik.

Description: ThisCrazyLife and these Cats got off to a rough start.
He thought they were walkin around the block
actin like strays and didn't like it.
They made him chase them around until they got away.
A little while later their paths crossed again.
ThisCrazyLife realized they were
just trying to find their way
and they were really cute and friendly.
and they found out he loves cats and has two of his own.
The Cats and Crazy became attached and are now great pals
who wanted to mint their story
and share it with the community.
